### Health check
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/

### Next ETA for a stop
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/eta/next?stop_id=MRT_DUKUH_ATAS&current_time=2026-05-23T07:20:00&limit=3

### Transfer optimization
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/optimizer/transfer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from_stop_id": "TJ_DUKUH_ATAS",
  "to_stop_id": "MRT_DUKUH_ATAS",
  "current_time": "2026-05-23T07:20:00",
